{"chunks": [{"text": "# 1-dars: Namuna kirish darsi (test uchun)\n\n## Mavzu: Python o'zgaruvchilari\n\nPython'da o'zgaruvchi yaratish juda oson. Siz shunchaki nom va qiymat yozasiz:\n\n```python\nism = \"Ali\"\nyosh = 25\nboyi = 1.75\n```\n\nPython o'zgaruvchi turini avtomatik aniqlaydi. Bu — **dynamic typing** deb ataladi.\n\n## O'zgaruvchi nomlash qoidalari\n\n1. Faqat harf, raqam va `_` belgisidan foydalanish mumkin\n2. Raqam bilan boshlanmasligi kerak\n3. Probel ishlatib bo'lmaydi\n4. O'zbek harflari texnik jihatdan ishlaydi, lekin tavsiya etilmaydi\n\n**To'g'ri misollar:** `talaba_ismi`, `yosh`, `_yashirin`, `son1`\n**Noto'g'ri misollar:** `1-talaba`, `talaba ismi`, `talaba!`\n\n## Uy vazifasi\n\n3 ta o'zgaruvchi yarating: ismingiz, yoshingiz va boyingiz. Keyin ularni `print()` orqali ekranga chiqaring.", "source": "01-namuna-dars.md", "chunk_id": 0}], "embeddings": [[-0.015530151315033436, -0.007839513942599297, 0.017755720764398575, -0.05553729459643364, -0.0016113988822326064, 0.0020374732557684183, -0.006256811786442995, 0.007008897606283426, -0.0002185064513469115, 0.012066222727298737, -0.02060334011912346, -0.02292812243103981, -0.012228371575474739, 0.0054541765712201595, 0.1377985030412674, 0.007502477150410414, -0.004592879209667444, -0.0005971310893073678, -0.002959473291411996, -0.01838817447423935, 0.0049483273178339005, 0.006576274987310171, 0.007611468434333801, -0.002530382014811039, -0.003417858388274908, 0.0011677115689963102, 0.008394242264330387, 0.018588552251458168, 0.018134668469429016, -0.012230065651237965, -0.0023359765764325857, 0.01349660661071539, 0.0029627333860844374, 0.018664764240384102, -0.015052298083901405, 0.006066886708140373, 0.029306653887033463, 0.008927630260586739, -0.008316285908222198, 0.02554026059806347, -0.0184266846626997, -0.0007207745220512152, -0.004248973447829485, -0.011858494020998478, 0.01058149803429842, 0.0007522476953454316, 0.003706716699525714, -0.030384300276637077, 0.001819421537220478, 0.027082005